quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  7,188,keh do ke mein apne faiday aur nuqsaan ka kuch bhi ikhtiyar nahi rakhta magar jo allah chahay aur agar mein ghaib ki baatein jaanta hota to bohat se faiday jama karleta aur mujh ko koi takleef nah pahunchti. mein to mominon ko dar aur khushkhabri sunanay wala hon
  7,189,woh khuda hi to hai jis ne tum ko 1 shakhs se pedakiya aur is se is ka jora banaya taakay is se raahat haasil kere. so jab woh is ke paas jata hai to usay halka sa hamal reh jata hai aur woh is ke sath chalti phurti hai. phir jab kuch boojh maloom karti yani bacha pait mein bara hota hai to dono miyan biwi apne perwar-digaar khuday-e azzwajal se iltija karte hain ke agar to hamein sahih o salim ( bacha ) day ga to hum tairay shukar guzar hon ge
  7,190,jab woh un ko sahih o salim ( bacha ) deta hai to is ( bachay ) mein jo woh un ko deta hai is ka shareek muqarrar karte hain. jo woh shirk karte hain ( khuda ka rutba ) is se buland hai
  7,191,kiya woh aison ko shareek banatay hain jo kuch bhi peda nahi kar saktay aur khud peda kiye jatay hain
  7,192,aur nah un ki madad ki taaqat rakhtay hain aur nah apni hi madad kar saktay hain
  7,193,agar tum un ko seedhay raste ki taraf bulaao to tumhara kaha nah manen. tumahray liye barabar hai ke tum un ko bulaao ya chupkay ho raho
  7,194,( mushrako ) jin ko tum khuda ke siwa pkarte ho woh tumhari terhan ke bande hi hain ( acha ) tum un ko poukaro agar sachey ho to chahiye ke woh tum ko jawab bhi den
  7,195,bhala un ke paon hain jin se chalein ya haath hain jin se pakren ya ankhen hain jin se dekhen ya kaan hain jin se sunen? keh do ke apne sharikon ko bulalo aur mere baray mein ( jo ) tadbeer ( karni ho ) karlo aur mujhe kuch mohlat bhi nah do ( phir dekho ke woh merakiya kar saktay hain )
